import React, { useState } from "react"; import styles from "./signup2.css" import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; const Signup = () =>{ const Register = ()=>{ const [formData,setformData] = useState({ Email:'', Password:'', RePass:'', MobileNumber:'', Location:'' }); const [error,seterror] = useState({ Email:'', Password:'', RePass:'' }); const [user,setuser] = useState([]); const handleInputChange = (e)=>{ const {name,value} = e.target; setformData({ ...formData,[name]:value, }); }; const validate = ()=>{ if(formData.Password != formData.RePass){ seterror({ ...error,RePass:'Password does not match' }); return false; } return true; }; const isEmailExists = (Email)=>{ return user.some((user)=>user.Email === Email) } } return <> <> SIGNUP PAGE
REGISTER
Your password must be 8-20 characters long, contain letters and numbers, and must not contain spaces, special characters, or emoji.
{/* */} Submit
} export default Signup;
